Cash Bash 2023

Saturday, September 24, 2023 @ 1:00 PM EST

1st Prize: $10,000

2nd Prize: $2,500

13 Prizes: $500.00

10 Prizes: $100.00

Rules

  • $100.00 Per Ticket. Winner need not be present.
  • All numbers will be drawn on September 23rd, 2023 at the Mt. Sinai Fire Department, Station 1, 133 Mount Sinai Avenue.
  • Gates will open at 1pm and event will run until 5pm, rain or shine.
  • All winning numbers are re-entered for additional prizes.
  • Only 2 ADULTS per ticket will be allowed entry. Please bring your own lawn chair.
  • Only (up to) 500 tickets will be sold. Tickets must be shown at the gate for entry.
  • No one under 21 will be admited. NO EXCEPTIONS!!!
  • All tickets will be mailed to the address you put on the application once your payment clears. Tickets purchased after 9/1/2022 can be picked up at the gate with photo ID.
  • You can choose your personal number 1-500. If a ticket number choice is not available, a random number will then be sent to you in its place.
  • For additional questions contact: Cash Bash Committee at: msfdcashbash@gmail.com
  • Entertainment, BBQ and drinks will be available during drawing, all included with ticket purchase.
  • IF LESS THAN 500 TICKETS ARE SOLD, ALL PRIZES WILL BE PRORATED AT 60% OF TOTAL SOLD

Enter for a chance to win an additional free ticket for five more dollars, select in drop down.

Tickets

IF LESS THAN 500 TICKETS ARE SOLD, ALL PRIZES WILL BE PRO-RATED AT 60% OF TOTAL SOLD.

Enter for a chance to win an additional free ticket for five more dollars, select in drop down.

Cash Bash Ticket

1st Prize: $10,000

2nd Prize: $2,500

10 Prizes: $100.00

 
  1. $100.00 Per Ticket. Winner need not be present.
  2. All numbers will be drawn on September 23rd, 2023 at the Mt. Sinai Fire Department, Station 1, 133 Mount Sinai Avenue.
  3. Gates will open at 1 pm and event will run until 5 pm, rain or shine.
  4. All winning numbers are re-entered for additional prizes.
  5. Only 2 ADULTS per ticket will be allowed entry. Please bring your own lawn chair.
  6. Only (up to) 500 tickets will be sold. Tickets must be shown at the gate for entry.
  7. No one under 21 will be admited. NO EXCEPTIONS!!!
  8. All tickets will be mailed to the address you put on the application once your check clears. Tickets purchased after 9/1/2023 can be picked up at the gate with photo ID.
  9. You can choose your personal number 1-500. If a ticket number choice is not available, a random number will then be sent to you in its place.
  10. For additional questions contact: Cash Bash Committee at: msfdcashbash@gmail.com
  11. Entertainment, BBQ and drinks will be available during drawing, all included with ticket purchase.

13 Prizes: $500.00

10 Prizes: $100.00

 
  1. $100.00 Per Ticket. Winner need not be present.
  2. All numbers will be drawn on September 23rd, 2023 at the Mt. Sinai Fire Department, Station 1, 133 Mount Sinai Avenue.
  3. Gates will open at 1 pm and event will run until 5 pm, rain or shine.
  4. All winning numbers are re-entered for additional prizes.
  5. Only 2 ADULTS per ticket will be allowed entry. Please bring your own lawn chair.
  6. Only (up to) 500 tickets will be sold. Tickets must be shown at the gate for entry.
  7. No one under 21 will be admited. NO EXCEPTIONS!!!
  8. All tickets will be mailed to the address you put on the application once your check clears. Tickets purchased after 9/1/2023 can be picked up at the gate with photo ID.
  9. You can choose your personal number 1-500. If a ticket number choice is not available, a random number will then be sent to you in its place.
  10. For additional questions contact: Cash Bash Committee at: msfdcashbash@gmail.com
  11. Entertainment, BBQ and drinks will be available during drawing, all included with ticket purchase.
  12. IF LESS THAN 500 TICKETS ARE SOLD, ALL PRIZES WILL BE PRORATED AT 60% OF TOTAL SOLD

Enter for a chance to win an additional free ticket for five more dollars, select in drop down.

Winner Contact #
Cash Bash Ticket

1st Prize: $10,000

2nd Prize: $2,500

13 Prizes: $500.00

10 Prizes: $100.00

 
  1. $100.00 Per Ticket. Winner need not be present.
  2. All numbers will be drawn on September 23rd, 2023 at the Mt. Sinai Fire Department, Station 1, 133 Mount Sinai Avenue.
  3. Gates will open at 1 pm and event will run until 5 pm, rain or shine.
  4. All winning numbers are re-entered for additional prizes.
  5. Only 2 ADULTS per ticket will be allowed entry. Please bring your own lawn chair.
  6. Only (up to) 500 tickets will be sold. Tickets must be shown at the gate for entry.
  7. No one under 21 will be admited. NO EXCEPTIONS!!!
  8. All tickets will be mailed to the address you put on the application once your check clears. Tickets purchased after 9/1/2023 can be picked up at the gate with photo ID.
  9. You can choose your personal number 1-500. If a ticket number choice is not available, a random number will then be sent to you in its place.
  10. For additional questions contact: Cash Bash Committee at: msfdcashbash@gmail.com
  11. Entertainment, BBQ and drinks will be available during drawing, all included with ticket purchase.
  12. IF LESS THAN 500 TICKETS ARE SOLD, ALL PRIZES WILL BE PRORATED AT 60% OF TOTAL SOLD

  3. Gates will open at 1 pm and event will run until 5 pm, rain or shine.
  4. All winning numbers are re-entered for additional prizes.
  5. Only 2 ADULTS per ticket will be allowed entry. Please bring your own lawn chair.
  6. Only (up to) 500 tickets will be sold. Tickets must be shown at the gate for entry.
  7. No one under 21 will be admited. NO EXCEPTIONS!!!
  8. All tickets will be mailed to the address you put on the application once your check clears. Tickets purchased after 9/1/2023 can be picked up at the gate with photo ID.
  9. You can choose your personal number 1-500. If a ticket number choice is not available, a random number will then be sent to you in its place.
  10. For additional questions contact: Cash Bash Committee at: msfdcashbash@gmail.com
  11. Entertainment, BBQ and drinks will be available during drawing, all included with ticket purchase.
  12. IF LESS THAN 500 TICKETS ARE SOLD, ALL PRIZES WILL BE PRORATED AT 60% OF TOTAL SOLD

1st Prize: $10,000

2nd Prize: $2,500

13 Prizes: $500.00

10 Prizes: $100.00

 
  1. $100.00 Per Ticket. Winner need not be present.
  2. All numbers will be drawn on September 23rd, 2023 at the Mt. Sinai Fire Department, Station 1, 133 Mount Sinai Avenue.
  3. Gates will open at 1 pm and event will run until 5 pm, rain or shine.
  4. All winning numbers are re-entered for additional prizes.
  5. Only 2 ADULTS per ticket will be allowed entry. Please bring your own lawn chair.
  6. Only (up to) 500 tickets will be sold. Tickets must be shown at the gate for entry.
  7. No one under 21 will be admited. NO EXCEPTIONS!!!
  8. All tickets will be mailed to the address you put on the application once your check clears. Tickets purchased after 9/1/2023 can be picked up at the gate with photo ID.
  9. You can choose your personal number 1-500. If a ticket number choice is not available, a random number will then be sent to you in its place.
  10. For additional questions contact: Cash Bash Committee at: msfdcashbash@gmail.com
  11. Entertainment, BBQ and drinks will be available during drawing, all included with ticket purchase.
  12. IF LESS THAN 500 TICKETS ARE SOLD, ALL PRIZES WILL BE PRORATED AT 60% OF TOTAL SOLD

Enter for a chance to win an additional free ticket for five more dollars, select in drop down.

  1. $100.00 Per Ticket. Winner need not be present.
  2. All numbers will be drawn on September 23rd, 2023 at the Mt. Sinai Fire Department, Station 1, 133 Mount Sinai Avenue.
  3. Gates will open at 1 pm and event will run until 5 pm, rain or shine.
  4. All winning numbers are re-entered for additional prizes.
  5. Only 2 ADULTS per ticket will be allowed entry. Please bring your own lawn chair.
  6. Only (up to) 500 tickets will be sold. Tickets must be shown at the gate for entry.
  7. No one under 21 will be admited. NO EXCEPTIONS!!!
  8. All tickets will be mailed to the address you put on the application once your check clears. Tickets purchased after 9/1/2023 can be picked up at the gate with photo ID.
  9. You can choose your personal number 1-500. If a ticket number choice is not available, a random number will then be sent to you in its place.
  10. For additional questions contact: Cash Bash Committee at: msfdcashbash@gmail.com
  11. Entertainment, BBQ and drinks will be available during drawing, all included with ticket purchase.
  12. IF LESS THAN 500 TICKETS ARE SOLD, ALL PRIZES WILL BE PRORATED AT 60% OF TOTAL SOLD

2nd Prize: $2,500

13 Prizes: $500.00

10 Prizes: $100.00

 
  1. $100.00 Per Ticket. Winner need not be present.
  2. All numbers will be drawn on September 23rd, 2023 at the Mt. Sinai Fire Department, Station 1, 133 Mount Sinai Avenue.
  3. Gates will open at 1 pm and event will run until 5 pm, rain or shine.
  4. All winning numbers are re-entered for additional prizes.
  5. Only 2 ADULTS per ticket will be allowed entry. Please bring your own lawn chair.
  6. Only (up to) 500 tickets will be sold. Tickets must be shown at the gate for entry.
  7. No one under 21 will be admited. NO EXCEPTIONS!!!
  8. All tickets will be mailed to the address you put on the application once your check clears. Tickets purchased after 9/1/2023 can be picked up at the gate with photo ID.
  9. You can choose your personal number 1-500. If a ticket number choice is not available, a random number will then be sent to you in its place.
  10. For additional questions contact: Cash Bash Committee at: msfdcashbash@gmail.com
  11. Entertainment, BBQ and drinks will be available during drawing, all included with ticket purchase.
  12. IF LESS THAN 500 TICKETS ARE SOLD, ALL PRIZES WILL BE PRORATED AT 60% OF TOTAL SOLD

Enter for a chance to win an additional free ticket for five more dollars, select in drop down.

13 Prizes: $500.00

10 Prizes: $100.00

 
  1. $100.00 Per Ticket. Winner need not be present.
  2. All numbers will be drawn on September 23rd, 2023 at the Mt. Sinai Fire Department, Station 1, 133 Mount Sinai Avenue.
  3. Gates will open at 1 pm and event will run until 5 pm, rain or shine.
  4. All winning numbers are re-entered for additional prizes.
  5. Only 2 ADULTS per ticket will be allowed entry. Please bring your own lawn chair.
  6. Only (up to) 500 tickets will be sold. Tickets must be shown at the gate for entry.
  7. No one under 21 will be admited. NO EXCEPTIONS!!!
  8. All tickets will be mailed to the address you put on the application once your check clears. Tickets purchased after 9/1/2023 can be picked up at the gate with photo ID.
  9. You can choose your personal number 1-500. If a ticket number choice is not available, a random number will then be sent to you in its place.
  10. For additional questions contact: Cash Bash Committee at: msfdcashbash@gmail.com
  11. Entertainment, BBQ and drinks will be available during drawing, all included with ticket purchase.
  12. IF LESS THAN 500 TICKETS ARE SOLD, ALL PRIZES WILL BE PRORATED AT 60% OF TOTAL SOLD

Enter for a chance to win an additional free ticket for five more dollars, select in drop down.

Winner Contact #
Cash Bash Ticket

1st Prize: $10,000

2nd Prize: $2,500

13 Prizes: $500.00

10 Prizes: $100.00

 
  1. $100.00 Per Ticket. Winner need not be present.
  2. All numbers will be drawn on September 23rd, 2023 at the Mt. Sinai Fire Department, Station 1, 133 Mount Sinai Avenue.
  3. Gates will open at 1 pm and event will run until 5 pm, rain or shine.
  4. All winning numbers are re-entered for additional prizes.
  5. Only 2 ADULTS per ticket will be allowed entry. Please bring your own lawn chair.
  6. Only (up to) 500 tickets will be sold. Tickets must be shown at the gate for entry.
  7. No one under 21 will be admited. NO EXCEPTIONS!!!
  8. All tickets will be mailed to the address you put on the application once your check clears. Tickets purchased after 9/1/2023 can be picked up at the gate with photo ID.
  9. You can choose your personal number 1-500. If a ticket number choice is not available, a random number will then be sent to you in its place.
  10. For additional questions contact: Cash Bash Committee at: msfdcashbash@gmail.com
  11. Entertainment, BBQ and drinks will be available during drawing, all included with ticket purchase.
  12. IF LESS THAN 500 TICKETS ARE SOLD, ALL PRIZES WILL BE PRORATED AT 60% OF TOTAL SOLD
